{"type":"text","timestamp":1781763885451,"sessionID":"ses_1269bed27ffeaBceEWnTAdPS3b","part":{"id":"prt_ed9674918001NSgl8y6KMNwIJf","messageID":"msg_ed966d4f1001wBwg4rEzIBU75j","sessionID":"ses_1269bed27ffeaBceEWnTAdPS3b","type":"text","text":"The second adjacent issue is scope drift rather than tenant leakage: the community fallback re-applies tenant/user/agent filtering, but not the caller’s `specFolder`, tier, or context filters before appending fallback rows. I’m writing the review state, iteration, dashboard, and synthesis report now.","time":{"start":1781763885336,"end":1781763885450},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0515c977b6cc4859016a338f2d4d8c819184ed2a31b75ed0ed","phase":"commentary"}}}}
